          <td class="post-content">
            <div class="post-content-inner">
              
              Onions are excellent.  I love them raw, sliced thin on sandwiches or in salads, caramelized, on tacos, in French onion soup, pretty much everywhere.<br /><br />For a long time I thought I disliked onion rings.  Then I had incredible onion rings at a pub one night and realized that I loved excellent onion rings, I'd just been receiving crap onion rings up until that point.

              

              
              
            </div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
