              If onions were a girl, I might consider marrying them.<br /><br />That's how much I love onions.<br /><br />Pickled, sauteed, grilled, fried, or raw.  Yum.<br /><br />Also, red, yellow, or white...yum.  The white ones get kind of bitey sometimes.  I like red the best, probably.<br /><br />And wiki tells me that the Chinese eat 6 times as many onions as the US does.  This surprises me, because when I think of onions, I think of soffrito, mirepoix, or &quot;the trinity&quot;.  Not chinese food.

              

              
              
