              I like the taste of onions, but dislike the texture.<br />So minced onions in food never draws a complaint from me but 1/4 of an onion of a burger?  EWWW.  <br /><br />I often order food with onions, then take them off. It leaves a gentle taste with no texture.<br /><br />If (as in your poll) I am only allowed WITH onions or WITHOUT, I have to vote without.  Too bad, as I like the taste of onions.

              

              
              
